<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٤٦ ... سُورَةُ الأَحْقَافِ ... آياتها ٣٥ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَجَلٍ مُّسَمًّى}</span> ...<span class="c5"> هُوَ:</span> وَقْتُ فَنَائِهِمَا إَذَا قَامَتِ القِيَامَةُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَهُمْ شِرْكٌ}</span> ... شِرْكَةٌ وَنَصِيبٌ مَعَ اللهِ تَعَالَى فِي خَلْقِ السَّمَوَاتِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَثَارَةٍ}</span> ... بَقِيَّةٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَمَنْ أَضَلُّ}</span> ... لَا أَحَدَ أَضَلُّ، وَأَجْهَلُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{افْتَرَاهُ}</span> ... اخْتَلَقَهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تُفِيضُونَ فِيهِ}</span> ... تَقُولُونَ فيِ القُرْآنِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِدْعًا مِّنْ الرُّسُلِ}</span> ... أَوَّلَ رُسُلِ اللهِ إِلَى خَلْقِهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَرَأَيْتُمْ}</span> ... أَخْبِرُونِي.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَشَهِدَ شَاهِدٌ}</span> ... كَعَبْدِ اللهِ بْنِ سَلَامٍ - رضي الله عنه -.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِفْكٌ قَدِيمٌ}</span> ... كَذِبٌ مَاثُورٌ عَنِ النَّاسِ الأَقْدَمِينَ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{إِمَامًا}</span> ... هَادِيًا يَاتَمُّونَ بِهِ، وَيَعْمَلُونَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُّصَدِّقٌ}</span> ... لِكُتُبٍ قَبْلَهُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{اسْتَقَامُوا}</span> ... ثَبَتُوا عَلَى الإِيمَانِ وَالطَّاعَةِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَوَصَّيْنَا}</span> ... أَمَرْنَاهُ، وَأَلْزَمْنَاهُ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كُرْهًا}</span> ... عَلَى مَشَقَّةٍ، وَتَعَبٍ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>